{
  "stem": "26465.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took us there, also again, on the roll call, inside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stood there for quite a long while, tired, some people who were falling.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some people were almost dying, and some people were disposed of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were so tired and worn-out that everybody probably wished to be dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, finally, they drove us into one of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there we stayed for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or stayed till 9th of-- I think the 9th or 10th of December, in '42.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in '42--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In between, what were we doing?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Quite a lot of women were taken out, chosen at random from the-- from the barrack, to do certain services to work around the kitchen and around the premises, cleaning.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- What did you do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was mostly cleaning a place where the German-- the Gestapo-- were having their suppers or dinners.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, after everything was cleaned, we were cleaning the floors-- washing the floors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were washing even the walls and the doors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, around that barrack-- 'barrack'-- the building, rather, because this I would not call a 'barrack.' It was a cement building, it's-- And sometimes you were taken to the kitchen, to watch the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Around the kitchen they were throwing the-- the-- all kinds of filth outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if they didn't throw it around-- so I had to clean it around-- the-- the-- the mess around there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We always had some different kind of chores to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at times we were, of course-- whenever we did something not to their liking or being just simply exhausted-- too exhausted to do it, and we just started hesitating, you know-- resting a little bit.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
